imdb.plot outline: Fishing Wild takes its viewers to the world s wildest and most remote fishing locations including North Africa, Alaska, Canada, Papua New Guinea, the Amazon Basin, Seychelles, Argentina and the depths of the Australian Outback. Exotic locations, stunning footage and expert advice on both fishing, photography and travel combine to make Fishing Wild unique amongst fishing programs worldwide.
